data.description: This charming home located in the desirable Stonebrier at Oakleaf Plantation includes 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. Tile floors can be found throughout. The open, split bedroom floor plan is bright & boasts tile floors in all rooms. The eat-in kitchen features a beautiful tile backsplash. The master bedroom has a gorgeous tray ceiling and the connecting master bath includes double sinks, a large garden tub, shower and a really large walk in closet with shelving. The family room overlooks the fenced back yard. Located close to shopping, restaurants, entertainment & more, this home is a GREAT find!
